             <div class="body">Very good thoughts. I don't believe, however, that the virus was set free intentionally. Rather, some scientists detected a new flu virus, the media got the news and spread them widely, then the people, ignorant of medical facts, panicked and demanded that the politicians do something. The politicians had to follow, and the people, moved by anxiety, readily gave up their freedom.

But after all, it is a reaction by material nature under the direction of the Supreme Lord to the uncountable acts of violence that mankind is committing against nature, especially in the realm of animal abuse. For Krishna's devotees the sudden peace all over is a good chance to go inside while they can't go outside.</div>
