        <article class="comment">
            <header class="clearfix">
                <div class="meta">
                    <h3>Manidhara Das To Vaidyanath Das</h3>
                    <span class="date">
                        28 Mar 2020
                    </span>
                </div>
            </header>
             <div class="body">Well, the conspiration theories are now surely as rampant as the virus itself. As we remember Srila Prabhupada, already during His stay with us, facing Hong Kong flue epidemy, (yes, He comments rather sarcastically that "he also took some vaccination"), and in His childhood seeing massive riots in Calcutta with heaps of dead bodies laying around, leprosy colonies and other type of maladies affecting people in great numbers (how many He must have met in His pharmacy!), He finally summed it up saying, "it is maya, it is all maya who is behind all this".

But there is evidence that already 2015 an article in a "scientific" magazine appeared, describing exactly the nature of coronavirus carried by bats. At that time the virus itself was described as not being able to affect humans, but same time the scientists proudly announced, that they succeeded in making it “compatible” with human cells.

And so the biological laboratories run by demons are certainly capable to produce a new variation of already dangerous natural product and "mess it up" as usually scientists do. After messing it up they will dare to consume even more money derived finally from innocent citizens in outrageous way, so "they can offer the solution to the problem". It is like beating somebody up, change the dress and appear again on the scene as the ambulance driver. 
The one who discovered x-rays died on her own discovery, the atomic bomb is another "scientific contribution" to further destruction of mankind, and so we can only marvel at this latest scientific "accident" effecting lives of so many. Regardless if such disaster is "accidental" or was intentionally staged, as usually few may profit greatly from the misery of so many others. We are dominated by class of people who will try to turn everything in profit for themselves, not hesitating to eliminate so many on the way.

Finally Srila Prabhupada always pointed to the fact that soon or later we will die anyway, and so death is the real problem, not the virus.
Those who are pious will remember it now while the impious ones will try to solve the material problem by material means, turning out either to be helpless or making things even worse.

Such determined souls like yourself will know that we are all infected by virus of maya, and the only remedy is finally the chanting of the Holy Name and hearing of Srila Prabhupada's nectarean instructions. And so when the Holy Name appears, the sinful ones will flee in all directions while the pious ones fall at Krsna's lotus feet, holding Them in their hearts even more tightly. Thanks to the virus we will know who is who :-)


Thank you for commenting! A comment from a wonderful godbrother is always inspiring!

Your servant Manidhara das</div>
